I made this for a tropical-themed office party. It never made it to the office as I threw it out. Even though I followed the recipe, apparently my technique was off because it came out as a badly colored, watery mess. Even that wouldn't have stopped me if the taste was there, and it was not. This recipe cost me about $40 to throw out.

